Introduction

Injun is a South Korean singer New Ways Company. He is a member of the upcoming boy group ASC2NT and a former member of the boy groups XING and DGNA.

He made his acting debut in 2017 as the main role in Power Rangers Dino Force Brave.

In late 2024, New Ways Company announced that Injun would go on hiatus due to health problems.
